WEBVTT

00:11:29.640 --> 00:11:31.000
by two degrees Celsius.

00:11:34.440 --> 00:11:35.640
By the way,

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:39.376
I've requested the TED organizers here

00:11:39.400 --> 00:11:43.280
to turn up the heat in here
by two degrees,

00:11:44.520 --> 00:11:47.336
so if some of you
are feeling warmer than usual,

00:11:47.360 --> 00:11:48.560
you know who to blame.

00:11:51.520 --> 00:11:55.160
It's crucial that all of us
keep our commitments.

00:11:55.600 --> 00:11:57.056
As far as Bhutan is concerned,

00:11:57.080 --> 00:12:00.520
we will keep our promise
to remain carbon neutral.